An end-to-end **Machine Learning movie recommendation system** built with a production-style architecture and MLOps practices. The system recommends movies to users based on historical ratings using **Collaborative Filtering (SVD)**.

## 🚀 Features
- Modular ML pipeline
- Hyperparameter tuning
- FastAPI inference API
- Streamlit UI
- Docker containerization
- CI pipeline with GitHub Actions
- Kubernetes deployment (next phase)

## ⚙️ ML Pipeline
Data Ingestion → Data Validation → Data Preprocessing → Feature Engineering → Train/Test Split → Model Training → Hyperparameter Tuning → Model Evaluation → Model Saving

Model: **SVD (Matrix Factorization)**  
Metric: **RMSE**

## 🌐 API Example
`GET /recommend?user_id=1`

Response example:
- Toy Story (1995) → 4.76  
- Seven (1995) → 4.43  

## 🐳 Docker
Build image:
docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t movie-recommender .

Run container:
docker run -p 8000:8000 movie-recommender

## 🛠 Tech Stack
Python • FastAPI • Streamlit • Scikit-Learn • Surprise (SVD) • Docker • GitHub Actions • Kubernetes

## 📊 Dataset
MovieLens Dataset